    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000"> New Features<br> ------------<br> - You can specify which Vim instance to edit the file by setting a variable in your .vimrc (i.e. let g:outlook_servername = 'OUTLOOK')<br> <br> Bug Fixes<br> ---------<br> - For some (international?) Windows versions, there were errors when (or a failure) editing the file.&nbsp;&nbsp;Needed to escape the backslashes of the filename.<br></td>
</tr>
